Project Overview
This repository contains an end to end Power BI project analyzing the sales performance and customer distribution of a cookie company. The project transforms raw Excel data into an interactive dashboard to track revenue growth, shipping trends, and market share across different countries.

üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack & Skills
Tool: Power BI Desktop.

ETL/Preprocessing: Power Query (Data cleaning, type conversion, and standardizing country names).

Data Modeling: Established a Star Schema by creating relationships between Customer and Order tables via Customer ID.

Visualization: clustered Bar chart, Line Charts, Donut Charts, and Interactive Slicers.

üìä Key Features
Revenue Performance: A high-level KPI card showing total revenue (currently at $513.98K).

Growth Trends: A line chart tracking the "Sum of Cookies Shipped" showing a significant upward trend between 2024 and 2025.

Market Segmentation: A donut chart visualizing revenue distribution across the United States, UK, Germany, and Canada.

Customer Analytics: A ranked bar chart showing the "Sum of Revenue by Customer Name" to identify top-tier clients.
